Angad Adventures Stories is a platform to share the best of stories from around the world. We believe 
there is always room for a story that can transport people to another place. You may be sitting at your
home right now behind a computer thinking you want to do this too. Every traveller has been at your place and the spark 
from a story has been all that it takes to get you out of your shell and explore the world.
Besides, Everyone loves a good story.
Those who tell the stories rule the world. When I first truly discovered the joy of sharing experiences was
the same day I wanted to inspire others to share there experiences as well.
Great stories happen to those who can tell them
